original_title: Whitney Cummings Presents: The OnlyFans Roast of Bert Kreischer
overview: Whitney Cummings roasts legendary comedian Bert "The Machine" Kreischer with the help of Jim Norton, Tom Segura, Big Jay Oakerson, Tony Hinchcliffe, Rachel Feinstein, Donnell Rawlings, Trevor Wallace, and some surprise celebrity guests.
title: Whitney Cummings Presents: The OnlyFans Roast of Bert Kreischer
